data.value: January - Mach -Best time to take a dip in sea.. Best time to visit the Central Hills.(Kandy,NuwaraEliya,Peradeniya Botanical Gardens). April - Sinhala New Year Season.. data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value:
1.Driving on an IDP or foreign national license is illegal in Srilanka, you need to get your non-Srilankan License verified in Sri Lanka.
2.All occupants of a moving vehicle should wear a seta belt.
3.Vehicles are driven in Left side.
4.Speed Limits , Urban - 50kph , Rural -70kph , Motorways - 100kph
5.Drink and Drive is strictly prohibited.

data.name: richTextBox3.Text
data.value: Burkha or any other complete face coverings are prohibited by the law. Passport or valied ID should be carried where ever you go. Carrying knives or any other weapons is a punishable offence. Should wear white colour top-bottom body covered cloths when visiting a Religious Place .
